<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM4.2">
<l>kāṭṭil vēṅkaṭaṅ kaṇṇa puranakar</l>
<l>vāṭṭa miṉṟi makiḻntuṟai vāmaṉaṉ</l>
<l>ōṭṭa rāvanteṉ kaippaṟṟi taṉṉōṭum</l>
<l>kūṭṭu mākilnī kūṭiṭu kūṭalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O circle! [You] be joined if</l>
<l rend="indent">Vāmana,</l>
<l rend="indent">who happily dwells free from trouble</l>
<l rend="indent">in Veṅkaṭam amidst the forest [and]</l>
<l rend="indent">in the town of Kaṇṇapuram,</l>
<l>comes running, grasps my hand, [and] unites [me] to Him!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
